> **Note:** The `email` attribute must be lowercase. Cycloid normalises email addresses to lowercase internally, which would cause Terraform to detect a perpetual diff if uppercase characters are provided. If your email input may contain uppercase characters (for example, from a variable or external data source), use Terraform's built-in [`lower()`](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/language/functions/lower) function:
>
> ```terraform
> resource "cycloid_organization_member" "tf_org_member" {
>   email          = lower(var.user_email)
>   role_canonical = "organization-admin"
> }
> ```

